---
name: Double Booking Guard System
description: Real AI-powered double booking prevention with auto-reschedule, auto-reassign, and email notifications
type: feature
---
- validate-booking edge function detects conflicts in real database
- On conflict: tries auto-reassignment to different resource of same type
- If no resource available: auto-reschedules to next available slot (up to 7 days ahead)
- If nothing available: auto-declines with explanation
- All conflicts logged to booking_conflicts table for DoubleBookingGuard UI
- Confirmation/decline emails sent via booking-reschedule email template
- DoubleBookingGuard component shows real conflict data from last 7 days
- Feature is industry-specific (uses industry labels for resources/clients/bookings)
- Industries with scheduling (all 8) benefit from this feature
